description:
Make sure you go to Datavision first to sign up and get your license key at http://datavision.io. Performance monitoring will never be the same after you do!  
            The package is available through your NuGet package manager and on the web at http://nuget.org/packages/Datavision.Agent

            Run: Install-Package Datavision.Agent

            Note: If you want to instrument more than one project in your solution, simply change the "Default project" in the package manager console and install the package.

            Visit http://rpm.datavision.io after your package deploy is complete to see your performance metrics.
summary: Includes the latest Datavision .NET Agent artifacts for deployment to your application's build output directory.
title: Datavision .NET Agent
